divs: Sighting DetailsRob aka BobbyD Garner, NC I was looking thru Facebook at a local artist that posted these pictures and she didn't notice the 2-4 lights above the train. I emailed her directly for the pictures and she just responded today... I have 4 pictures that I will include. You will notice that the object is to the left of the moon and it started off with 2 light and then went to 4. After speaking with Roger Marsh, he suggested that I submit them to you.
